し / 充電器なし → No battery / No charger | ストラップなし → No strap\n  箱なし / 元箱なし → No box | 説明書なし → No manual | メモリーカードなし → No memory card\n  ケースなし / ポーチなし → No case | レンズフードなし → No lens hood | アイカップなし → No eyecup\n  Title markers: append "No Box" "No Battery" "No Charger" etc. at end if space allows. Do NOT speculate about missing items not explicitly stated.\n- Describe operation/status only if clearly mentioned (tested/untested/issues).\n- Avoid evaluative adjectives (excellent, good, mint, used).\n- Exclude shipping/seller opinions/history/warranty.\n\nPRODUCTNAME\n- Format: [Brand] [Model] [Camera Type], English ASCII only.\n- Example: Canon AE-1 35mm SLR, Nikon FM2 35mm SLR, Leica M6 Rangefinder, Hasselblad 500CM Medium Format SLR\n\nCATEGORY\n- Digital Cameras (eBay ID: 31388) — DSLR, Mirrorless, Compact Digital\n- Film Cameras (eBay ID: 15230) — 35mm SLR, Rangefinder, Medium Format, Film Compact\n- Vintage SLR Film Cameras (eBay ID: 11720) — Vintage SLR cameras\n- Vintage TLR Film Cameras (eBay ID: 11721) — TLR / Twin-Lens Reflex\n- Camera Lenses (eBay ID: 3323) — Interchangeable lenses, including vintage lenses\n- Camera & Photo Accessories (eBay ID: 15200) — Straps, cases, filters, accessories\n- If unclear: N/A\nRoute: Digital camera (DSLR / Mirrorless / Compact Digital) → Digital Cameras. Film SLR / Rangefinder / Medium Format / Film Compact → Film Cameras. Vintage TLR → Vintage TLR Film Cameras. Lens only → Camera Lenses. Accessories → Camera & Photo Accessories.\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (exactly):\nTitle: ...\nDescription: ...\nProductName: ...\nCategory: ...\n\nVERIFICATION (must pass before returning):\n1. Title does not exceed 80 chars (eBay hard limit).\n2. Description <= 480 chars.\n3. Only ASCII letters/numbers/spaces and allowed symbols (& / : - . ,) used throughout.\n4. No CJK characters or emoji anywhere.\n5. Title front-loads brand within first 30 chars.\n6. Description first sentence contains brand + model + camera type keywords.\n7. ProductName uses real brand name (not N/A for brand).\n8. Lens specs in Title and Description match source exactly — do NOT modify focal length or aperture values.\n9. Condition/status words appear only if explicitly stated in source Japanese.\n10. No forbidden symbols in Title (only & / : - . , and \' for possessives are allowed).\n11. If source mentions any defect/malfunction, Description MUST include it.\n12. Every spec in the output (resolution, sensor, shutter count, mount, focal length) must have a corresponding source in the Japanese text. If not found in source, it must NOT appear in output.\n13. If shutter count keywords exist in source, include count in Description. If NO shutter count keywords in source, do NOT mention shutter count.\n14. No bootleg/replica/counterfeit language appears in any output field.\n15. If source implies replica/counterfeit camera, ALL fields must read [Cannot list].\n\nIf any check fails, regenerate until all pass.\n\nInput: ${fullText}\n' };


